I built an abstractive text summarizer using a fine-tuned DistilBART model trained on large datasets like XSum and CNN. It creates context-aware, length-controlled summaries for PDFs, DOCs, and TXT files. I set up a Dockerized Flask backend deployed on Hugging Face and built a clean Vite + Tailwind frontend for easy file uploads and results. This project helped me sharpen my NLP and deployment ski